title: Unbeatable Price! Close to UT and Downtown!
posting_body: ['For leasing info, call', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID# 73582', 'Where vibrant city living reaches new heights!', "This complex's newly renovated floor plans feature custom fixtures and cabinetry, brand new appliances, luxurious bedroom carpeting, and high-speed internet access.", 'Enjoy outdoor R&R in our wonderful community space, which includes a fire pit, BBQ area, multiple picnic tables, and a fun-filled pool area.', 'Your fur baby will also feel right at home in our pet-friendly atmosphere!', 'Best of all, our residents enjoy a short commute to the heart of Downtown Austin, which is home to a wide array of upscale and local dining, shopping, and entertainment.', 'Community Amenities:', 'Gated Community with Controlled Access', 'On-site Parking', 'Valet Trash', 'Sparkling Pool', 'Apartment Amenities:', 'W/D in unit', 'Brand new cabinets', 'Granite Countertops', 'Subway Tile Backsplash', 'Walk-in Closets', 'Ceiling fans throughout', 'Pet Friendly', "Don't miss out on the opportunity to live THIS close to the UT campus and Downtown Austin for THIS price!", 'Call me today,', 'show contact info', '!', 'Melinda Flemmings, Realtor']
